21:13.603 --> 21:15.695
♪ Ooh, I did a double take

21:15.695 --> 21:19.028
♪ Body like a summer day

21:19.028 --> 21:21.531
♪ Got a real mean undertow

21:21.531 --> 21:23.162
♪ Holds me down
Won't let me go

21:23.162 --> 21:26.496
♪ Love has got me
swept away

21:26.496 --> 21:30.670
♪ On a tide, tide,
tidal wave

21:30.670 --> 21:35.375
♪ A tide, tide, tidal wave ♪

21:40.510 --> 21:42.762
Xander, writing that song

21:42.762 --> 21:43.883
was the most
incredible thing

21:43.883 --> 21:45.515
anyone's ever done for me.

21:45.515 --> 21:47.727
And I once had a guy
offer to buy me an island.

21:47.727 --> 21:49.058
(CHUCKLES)
Wow.

21:49.058 --> 21:50.600
Like one of those little
Caribbean Islands?

21:50.600 --> 21:53.733
No. Manhattan.

21:53.733 --> 21:57.697
So I guess I'm not going with
that Free Hug Coupon Book
for your birthday.

21:57.697 --> 22:00.199
(CHUCKLES) Actually,
I would love that.

22:00.199 --> 22:01.781
In fact, I'll take one
right now.

22:01.781 --> 22:04.033
Oh. I'm sorry,
you don't have a coupon.

22:06.786 --> 22:10.660
Emma, I am so happy
we worked things out.

22:10.660 --> 22:13.833
You're so beautiful
and sweet.

22:15.334 --> 22:16.506
You're my everything.

22:17.667 --> 22:18.718
Thanks.

22:18.718 --> 22:19.959
Up top!

22:23.092 --> 22:24.384
Xander, guess what?

22:24.384 --> 22:27.597
We're up to a million
views on your video!

22:27.597 --> 22:29.969
My ChatSnap is exploding!

22:29.969 --> 22:33.563
Hey, I thought this song
wasn't supposed to be
about your ChatSnap.

22:33.563 --> 22:35.435
Come on, you know me
better than that.

22:36.646 --> 22:39.148
It's so cool that people
like my music so much.

22:39.148 --> 22:41.441
They do, but according
to the comments,

22:41.441 --> 22:43.903
they love Emma's
dancing even more.

22:43.903 --> 22:45.745
Oh, let's not
make this about me.

22:45.745 --> 22:47.747
This is about Xander.

22:47.747 --> 22:48.698
(WHISPERS)
Send me that link.

22:49.869 --> 22:52.081
Did anybody mention
my dancing?

22:52.622 --> 22:53.873
Ooh, read that one!

22:53.873 --> 22:55.875
It's from my  abuelo.

22:55.875 --> 22:57.877
"Jorge, get out
of the way,

22:57.877 --> 23:00.550
"and let  muy bonita
drop it like it's hot."
